---
title: Projects
Date: 2024-10-01
layout: base.njk

pagination:
  data: data.projects  # Correctly access projects inside the JSON
  size: 1             # Number of projects per page
  alias: project       # Alias for the current project in the loop
  addAllPagesToCollections: true
  permalink: "/pages/projects/project+{{ pagination.page }}/"  # Ensure each page has a unique URL
---

<h1>Our Projects</h1>
<p>At Cowhead Company and Associates, our projects focus on sustainable farming, ethical dairy production, and innovation. We prioritize eco-friendly practices, humane treatment of animals, and creating clean, high-quality dairy products. From sustainable farming methods to developing lactose-free options, we are committed to delivering responsible, environmentally conscious dairy that benefits both people and the planet.</p>
<p>Our projects throughout the years:</p><br>
<div class ="project-container">


<div class="project-cards">
    {% for project in pagination.items %}
    <h2 class="project-title">{{ project.title }}</h2>
    <p class="project-description">{{ project.description }}</p>
    <p class= "project-slogan"><strong>Slogan:</strong> {{ project.slogan }}</p>
    <p class ="project-date"> {{project.start_date}} - {{project.end_date}}</p>
    {% endfor %}
</div>

<!-- Pagination Controls -->
<div class="pagination">
    {% if pagination.href.previous %}
        <a href="{{ pagination.href.previous }}">Previous</a>
    {% endif %}
    <span>Page {{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }} of {{ 3 }}</span> <!-- pagination.pageNumber is zero-indexed, so add 1 -->
    {% if pagination.href.next %}
        <a href="{{ pagination.href.next }}">Next</a>
    {% endif %}
</div>
</div>